{
  "stem": "2980.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would cross our town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father was busy helping fix bicycles and fix cars, and fix wagons, and fix all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they would stream, tens of thousands of people, running, running east.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and-- and then they stayed for several days, and they were good.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They did not bother us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They would give out food to-- to the hungry, to refugees, and war, prisoners of war, Polish prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they kept saying, [NON-ENGLISH], here will be the-- the Russians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] is Russian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Says that they're going to leave, and the Russians will come instead.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we didn't understand.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They say the Germans are bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They don't look bad at all to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But we stayed from far.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But the Ukrainians came and welcomed them with flowers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the girls smiled and sang and danced with them, the Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But we kept away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were told that they're not our friends.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they stayed for about a week.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then they retreated, they left the town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the town remained without any military.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So Ukrainians came running in from all over and started looting, shooting, killing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So the Jewish groups organized themselves, and they started protecting the town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the-- some groups who were leftist built a gate to welcome the Russian, the Soviet Army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So at one point, the Polish soldiers which were running amok, they were running wild.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They came to town, they saw the gate for the-- for the Russians, the welcoming gate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they went through the town, and they shot every Jew they found.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they found-- they shot about to 10, 12 people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Fathers and sons, and people who put their heads to the window, they would just shoot them and kill them.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
